staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015320=^c:1486b0;小規模お祭り会場^c:pop;の進み具合はどうですか？
//[Reference] 'I think it should be quite straightforward to set up!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015330=設置に向けて一直線ですね！
//[Reference] 'Good work, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! This will serve very nicely!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015340=いいデキですね、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！これはとてもうまく機能しますよ！
//[Reference] 'There's just one final task we need to do to prepare.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015350=準備に必要な作業は残り1つです。
//[Reference] 'Could you perhaps put these up around the town? They're ^c:1486b0;flyers^c:pop; for the upcoming festival I've planned!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015360=こちらを町中に貼ってくれますか？計画している次のお祭りの^c:1486b0;チラシ^c:pop;です！
//[Reference] 'Just put them on walls around the town so that everyone knows what's going on!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015370=町中の壁に貼れば、みんなに何が始まるか知ってもらえます！
//[Reference] 'Still have a few more ^c:1486b0;flyers^c:pop; to put up, eh?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015380=まだ貼っていない^c:1486b0;チラシ^c:pop;を持っているのですか？
//[Reference] 'Well, no serious hurry, I suppose. It'll be a while before the festival kicks off.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015390=まぁ、緊急は要してはいません。お祭りの開催までもう少し時間がかかりますし。
//[Reference] 'Nice to see the marketing all set up and doing its job!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015400=いい兆候です。宣伝が完了して、効果が出てきました！
//[Reference] 'I've already had a few curious residents around asking about the harvest festival!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015410=すでに、収穫祭のこと興味深げに尋ねる住民も見かけましたよ！
//[Reference] 'This is a little something for your hard work! It's much nicer to have an assistant around, I must say.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015420=ちょっとしたものですが、働いてくれたお礼にどうぞ！そばにアシスタントを持つのはいいものですね。
//[Reference] 'Last time I tried something like this it didn't go too well...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015430=同じようなことを最後に試したときは、あまりうまくいきませんでした。
//[Reference] 'I'm beginning to think it was the lack of a good hard-worker like yourself!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015440=あなたのように働き者の人材不足のせいだと思えてきましたよ！
//[Reference] 'Ah, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;, perfect timing!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015450=あぁ、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;、ナイスタイミングです！
//[Reference] 'Preparations for the harvest festival are almost complete.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015460=収穫祭の準備はもうすぐ完了です。
//[Reference] 'There's just a few more bits and pieces we need—perhaps something you could help with?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015470=残ったのは、こまごました作業です。手伝っていただけませんか？
//[Reference] 'First, I'd like you to run on over to ^c:1486b0;{0-leif}^c:pop; and make sure he has his store ready to cope with the demand!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015480=まず、^c:1486b0;{0-leif}^c:pop;のもとへ行って、彼の店が需要に対処できるか確認してください！
//[Reference] 'Then, check in with ^c:1486b0;{0-aliza}^c:pop; for any last-minute construction problems.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015490=その次に、ここにきて建設に問題はないか^c:1486b0;{0-aliza}^c:pop;に確認します。
//[Reference] 'After that, make sure ^c:1486b0;{0-rowan}'s^c:pop; ^c:1486b0;sap^c:pop; supply is sufficiently stocked.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015500=それが終われば、^c:1486b0;{0-rowan}の^c:pop; ^c:1486b0;サップ^c:pop;の在庫は十分か確認してください。
//[Reference] 'With luck, that will mean we're all set to launch!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015510=うまくいけば、開催の準備が整ったということです！
//[Reference] 'Have you completed the errands I sent you on?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015520=頼んだお使いは全部終わりましたか？
//[Reference] 'You need to speak with ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop;, ^c:1486b0;Aliza^c:pop;, and ^c:1486b0;Rowan^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015530=^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;、^c:1486b0;アリザ^c:pop;、^c:1486b0;ローワン^c:pop;と話してくださいね。
//[Reference] 'It's just a case of confirming their preparedness.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015540=準備が整っているかちょっと確認するためですよ。
//[Reference] 'Everyone is fully prepared then? Excellent!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015550=みんな準備万端なんですね？すばらしい！
//[Reference] 'Let the festivities begin!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015560=お祭りをはじめましょう！
//[Reference] 'I'd suggest you try to participate as much as possible!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015570=できるだけお祭りに参加してくださいね！
//[Reference] 'The more people taking part, the more who will be intrigued and be enticed to participate!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015580=参加する人が多いほど、人目を引いて参加者を集めますよ！
//[Reference] 'Head over to the ^c:1486b0;small festival grounds^c:pop; whenever you're ready!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015590=準備ができたらいつでも^c:1486b0;小規模お祭り会場^c:pop;に来てください！
//[Reference] 'How are you enjoying the harvest festival, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10015600=収穫祭は楽しんでいますか、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;？
