staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10021700=完成したら、石像を町に置きます。それから^c:1486b0;銘板^c:pop;で石像を指定してください！
//[Reference] 'I do hope those ^c:1486b0;statues^c:pop; will draw in more tourism than our previous attempt...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10021800=以前試したときよりも、^c:1486b0;石像^c:pop;が旅行者の目に留まるといいのですが…
//[Reference] 'Excellent! Rather awe-inspiring, I must say!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10021900=いいですね！とても気高い雰囲気ですよ！
//[Reference] 'I have it on good authority that our first tourists have arrived too!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10022000=確かな筋から最初の旅行者が到着すると聞きました！
//[Reference] 'Perhaps you could speak with them and gather their feedback?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10022100=旅行者に話しかけて、感想を集めてくれますか？
//[Reference] 'It could be invaluable to ensuring their investment!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10022200=投資を集めるなら、貴重な情報ですよ！
//[Reference] 'So what did the tourists have to say about our town?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10022300=それで、旅行者は町について何と？
//[Reference] 'Were they impressed? Have we secured investors?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10022400=気に入っていましたか？投資していただけそうですか？
//[Reference] 'They...weren't happy then? The statues were no good?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10022500=満足…してない？石像は気に入らなかったと？
//[Reference] 'I'm sorry, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;. It seems I might have wasted your time.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10022600=申し訳ない、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;。あなたの時間をムダにしてしまいました。
//[Reference] 'But...do you think you might be up to trying again?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10022700=ですが…また協力してくれますか？
//[Reference] 'Maybe if we had exactly the right statues and a little bit of luck...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10022800=観光客が喜ぶような石像だったら…
//[Reference] 'Maybe then someone would show a bit more interest in the town!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10022900=もっと島に興味を示してくれるのではないでしょうか！
//[Reference] 'Make sure you remove the previous two ^c:1486b0;statues^c:pop;...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10023000=以前建てた2つの^c:1486b0;石像^c:pop;をどかしてください…
//[Reference] 'These new ones might attract a more helpful crowd...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10023100=次の新しい石像は、もっと良い効果をもたらしてくれるといいんですが…
//[Reference] 'Don't forget to remove the two ^c:1486b0;statues^c:pop; you erected before.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10023200=以前建てた2つの^c:1486b0;石像^c:pop;は、忘れずどかしてくださいね。
//[Reference] 'They didn't seem to go down too well with the visitors...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10023300=あの2体は観光客の心に響かなかったようなので…
//[Reference] 'Nice job, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10023400=よくやってくれました、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;。
//[Reference] 'Now all we can do is hope.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10023500=後は祈るばかりです。
//[Reference] 'I'd suggest going to see how our latest tourist is finding the town.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10023600=新しい旅行者が町で気になっているものは何か確認してくれますか？
//[Reference] 'Perhaps this is one we might be able to convince...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10023700=これで納得できることでしょう…
//[Reference] 'I believe the new tourist is over by one of the ^c:1486b0;statues^c:pop; you placed.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10023800=新しく来た旅行者が、あなたの建てたどれか1つの^c:1486b0;石像^c:pop;へ立ち寄ってますように。
//[Reference] 'Do your best to convince him so we can keep the town flourishing!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10023900=がんばって旅行者に気に入ってもらえれば、町の賑わいは維持できますよ！
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! Wonderful news!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10024000=^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！すごいニュースです！
//[Reference] 'We found an investor!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10024100=投資家が見つかりました！
//[Reference] 'A strange man in a suit? Resorts? Glass offices?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10024200=スーツを着た妙な男？リゾート？ガラスのオフィス？
//[Reference] 'What on earth are you rambling on about?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10024300=とりとめもなく、何の話ですか？
//[Reference] 'Apparently, a local historian was passing through when you erected those ^c:1486b0;historic monuments^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10024400=どうやら、あなたが^c:1486b0;歴史的な記念碑^c:pop;を建てているときに、現地の歴史学者が通りがかったようなんです！
//[Reference] 'He immediately recognised their likenesses and realised that the island was central in some ancient war or other!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10024500=その人は肖像をすぐに認識して、古代戦争の中心にあった島だと悟ったと言ってました！
//[Reference] 'So now we're getting a grant as a world heritage site! Can you believe that?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10024600=そのおかげで、この島は世界遺産として補助金を受けるんですよ！信じられますか？
//[Reference] 'Fantastic work, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! I couldn't have done it without you!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10024700=見事な仕事ぶりでした、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！あなたなしではできなかったですよ！
//[Reference] 'You practically saved the entire town! Or, its financing at least!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10024800=実質、町全体を救ってくれたんです。少なくとも財政面では！
//[Reference] 'This is never going to be enough to repay what you've given us...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10024900=あなたの功績に対して、これではお返しに足らないと思いますが...
//[Reference] 'But maybe you'd appreciate the honour of being the one to place our ^c:1486b0;commemorative plaque^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10025000=^c:1486b0;記念碑の銘板^c:pop;を設置する名誉を受けてくれませんか？
//[Reference] 'Or not, of course! I leave that decision entirely up to you!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Mayor.line:10025100=もちろん、しなくてもかまいません。決定はあなた次第ですよ！
